article.description: — Setric Millner Jr. and RayJ Dennis scored 16 points apiece as Toledo romped to a 94-63 victory over Northern Illinois in Mid-American Conference play on Saturday.
article.headline: Millner, Dennis help Toledo rout Northern Illinois 94-63
article.linkText: Millner, Dennis help Toledo rout Northern Illinois 94-63
article.story: TOLEDO, Ohio -- — Setric Millner Jr. and RayJ Dennis scored 16 points apiece as Toledo romped to a 94-63 victory over Northern Illinois in Mid-American Conference play on Saturday. Ryan Rollins added 15 points and seven rebounds for the Rockets (11-4, 3-1). Ra'Heim Moss had 12 points as Toledo won for a sixth straight time at home. Kaleb Thornton had 12 points for the Huskies (3-8), who were playing their MAC opener.
